                    </div>
                    <span>This is a fabulous book. The results of each quilt is a surprise.  It is now my favorite type of quilt to explore.  Every quilter should try this technique at least once.  The book is easy and Ricky is very specific on the areas where you need to be casual and then areas that are to be very specific.  LOVE IT, LOVE IT!.  For the new and experienced quilter.  Batiks are perfect for this style.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Tesselations - Jinny Beyer</div>
                    <div>
