                    <span>This is one of the most fascinating books I've read on quilting and stitchery!!!  It covers everything from the architectural aspect along with the mathematical.  I have only been quilting for the past year and a half; and being self-taught,this book is phenomenal if you are looking for something totally strange and unusual!!!  It's pretty easy to follow - but you have to pay attention to details!!!!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great Book</div>
